*  129 - Closest minimal repro of beauty stmt 1074 crash:
*  *outer where outer = ARBNO(*cmd) where cmd = FENCE(alt|alt).
*  String chosen so backtrack into seal is forced.
        cmd   = FENCE('a' | 'ab')
        outer = ARBNO(*cmd)
        s = 'aab'
        s POS(0) *outer RPOS(0)                               :S(BAD)F(GOOD)
BAD     OUTPUT = 'unexpected match'                           :(END)
GOOD    OUTPUT = 'beauty-class FENCE seal held'
END
